<div class="container">

    <div class="row">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <hr>

                <h2 class="intro-text text-center">About Gr8Ladies Conference Grants</h2>
                <hr>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <p>Sometimes individuals or companies support our cause to get more diverse attendees and speakers at conferences by donating tickets or funds to help
                pay for underrepresented individuals to attend these events. In 2017, we started a program to award tickets and/or travel grants. The first one was for
                    <a href="http://greachconf.com">Greach</a>. We hope to have more available for future conferences.
                </p>

                <p>In addition, as the number of women increases at these Groovy conferences, we hope to host more Gr8Ladies events.  If you would like to help
                or organize one, email <a
                        href="mailto:volunteers@gr8ladies.org">volunteers@gr8ladies.org</a>
                    or <a href="http://goo.gl/forms/IsKbpzAyU2xU6Utq1" target="_blank">submit this form</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="box">
            <p>If tickets/travel awards are available currently, the application will be listed on
                <a href="https://diversitytickets.org/events" target="_blank">diversitytickets.org</a>.
            If you have any questions about the program, please email <a href="mailto:jenn@gr8ladies.org">jenn@gr8ladies.org</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <p class="text-center">If you are looking for an event where you might find other Gr8Ladies, we suggest:</p>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="col-lg-10 col-sm-12 col-lg-offset-1">
                        <a href="http://gr8conf.eu" target="_blank"><asset:image class="img-responsive"
                                                                 src="conferences/gr8confeu.png"
                                                                 alt="Gr8Conf Europe"/></a>

                        <p class="text-center">Gr8Conf Europe</p>
                    </div>

                    <p>Copenhagen, Denmark</p>

                    <p>May 31 - June 2, 2017</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="col-lg-10 col-sm-12 col-lg-offset-1">
                        <a href="http://gr8conf.us" target="_blank"><asset:image class="img-responsive"
                                                                 src="conferences/gr8confus.png"
                                                                 alt="Gr8Conf US"/></a>
                            <p class="text-center">Gr8Conf US</p>
                    </div>

                    <p>Minneapolis, MN, USA</p>

                    <p>July 26 - 28, 2017</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
